  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Single-site blood collection investigation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      45 Heart Failure patients will be recruited. Patients will provide a one-time blood sample
      specimen collection. Theses samples will be de-identified and provided for measurement of
      Galectin-3 on commercial platforms.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
