      <textblock>
        45 matched door serum and plasma. Samples set collected form individual Heart Failure
        patients for galecin-3 measurements
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Heart Failure patients New York Heart Association class able to provide (4) collection
             tube types Subjects &gt; 18 years old All subjects must provide informed consent and
             associated documentation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects that cannot tolerate blood withdrawal of 4 specimens collection tube tubes
             (approximately 40 mLs)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
